Create a settings.xml file in users home directory
<settings>
 <servers>
   <server>
      <id>my-repo-id</id>
      <username>admin</username>
      <password>1234</password>
   </server>
 </servers>
</settings>


id ---> repository id from pom.xml
username-----> nexus username
password-----> nexus password



java version used
******************
install both packages
openjdjk8-headless
openjdk8

Create docker image using dockerfile

Pulling docker image to nexus
*****************************
create a docker hosted repository in nexus with port 1111
docker login localhost:1111
docker tag  simple-java-app:latest localhost:1111/my-app:latest
docker push localhost:1111/my-app


